---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
import TwitterEmbed from '../../components/TwitterEmbed.astro';

const usageSnippet = `---
import { TwitterEmbed } from 'comet-astro';
---

<div class="space-y-6">
  <TwitterEmbed 
    tweetId="1354143047324299264" 
    variant="default"
    theme="auto"
  />
  
  <TwitterEmbed 
    tweetId="1354143047324299264" 
    variant="elevated"
    size="lg"
    privacyMode
  />
  
  <TwitterEmbed 
    tweetId="1354143047324299264" 
    variant="minimal"
    showConversation={false}
  />
</div>`;
---

<DocsLayout
  title="TwitterEmbed"
  description="Accessible Twitter embed component with AAA contrast, privacy controls, and comprehensive loading states."
>
  <section class="space-y-4">
    <p class="text-base text-slate-100">
      TwitterEmbed allows you to embed tweets in your application with full
      accessibility support, privacy controls, and responsive design. The
      component follows WCAG AAA guidelines with proper contrast ratios and
      comprehensive error handling.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-slate-200">
      Each variant includes semantic styling, configurable privacy modes, and
      enhanced loading states that provide clear feedback to all users.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 space-y-6">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Props</h2>
    <dl class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          tweetId
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Required. The Twitter status ID of the tweet to embed. Found in the
          tweet URL.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          variant?
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Visual style for the embed container. Choose <code>"default"</code>, <code
            >"minimal"</code
          >, <code>"bordered"</code>, or <code>"elevated"</code>. Defaults to <code
            >"default"</code
          >.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          theme?
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Twitter widget theme. Choose <code>"light"</code>, <code>"dark"</code
          >, or <code>"auto"</code>. Auto adapts to system theme. Defaults to <code
            >"auto"</code
          >.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          size?
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Size of the embed container. Choose <code>"sm"</code>, <code
            >"md"</code
          >, or <code>"lg"</code>. Defaults to <code>"md"</code>.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          width?
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Maximum width constraint. Choose <code>"compact"</code>, <code
            >"normal"</code
          >, or <code>"wide"</code>. Defaults to <code>"normal"</code>.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          showConversation?
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Whether to show the conversation thread. Defaults to <code>true</code
          >.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          showCards?
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Whether to show Twitter cards (images, videos). Defaults to <code
            >true</code
          >.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          privacyMode?
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Enable Do Not Track mode for enhanced privacy. Defaults to <code
            >false</code
          >.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          loadingText?
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Custom loading message. Defaults to <code>"Loading tweet..."</code>.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          errorText?
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Custom error message. Defaults to <code>"Failed to load tweet"</code>.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div
        class="space-y-1 rounded-lg border border-slate-700/75 bg-slate-900/60 p-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <dt
          class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-200"
        >
          className?
        </dt>
        <dd class="text-sm text-slate-200">
          Additional CSS classes to apply to the embed container.
        </dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </section>

