  <section class="mt-10 space-y-6">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Accessibility</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-slate-200">
      <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-900/30 p-4">
        <h3 class="font-medium text-slate-100 mb-2">Screen Reader Support</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-300">
          <li>• Uses <code>role="region"</code> with descriptive labels</li>
          <li>• Live regions announce loading and error states</li>
          <li>• Proper semantic markup for embedded content</li>
          <li>• Alternative text and fallback links for failed embeds</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-900/30 p-4">
        <h3 class="font-medium text-slate-100 mb-2">Keyboard Navigation</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-300">
          <li>
            • <kbd class="px-1 py-0.5 bg-slate-700 rounded text-xs">Tab</kbd> - Navigate
            to embed container
          </li>
          <li>
            • <kbd class="px-1 py-0.5 bg-slate-700 rounded text-xs"
              >Enter/Space</kbd
            > - Open tweet on Twitter
          </li>
          <li>• Focus indicators on container and interactive elements</li>
          <li>• Keyboard access to all embed controls and links</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-900/30 p-4">
        <h3 class="font-medium text-slate-100 mb-2">Visual Accessibility</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-300">
          <li>• WCAG AAA contrast ratios (9:1) for all text and controls</li>
          <li>• High contrast mode support with enhanced borders</li>
          <li>• Forced colors mode compatibility</li>
          <li>• Responsive design adapts to different screen sizes</li>
          <li>• Reduced motion support disables animations</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-900/30 p-4">
        <h3 class="font-medium text-slate-100 mb-2">Privacy & Security</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-300">
          <li>• Optional Do Not Track mode prevents tracking</li>
          <li>• Privacy notice when DNT is enabled</li>
          <li>• Secure iframe loading with proper attributes</li>
          <li>• Graceful degradation when scripts fail to load</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
